# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks

# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.

# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.

## Example Tasks

- [ ] Check email for urgent messages
- [ ] Review calendar for upcoming events (next 24-48h)
- [ ] Check weather if going out
- [ ] Monitor system status

## Notes

- Tasks are checked every 30 minutes by default
- Agent will reply HEARTBEAT_OK if nothing needs attention
- If there are actionable items, agent will report them
